    <entry>
      <title>CentOS7.5安装</title>
      <link href="2020/12/17/CentOS7.5%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/"/>
      <url>2020/12/17/CentOS7.5%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="centos-75安装"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#centos-75安装"></a> CentOS 7.5安装</h1><blockquote><p>主机系统：win10<br />系统镜像：CentOS 7.5(1804)<br />虚拟机软件：VMware Workstation 16 Pro<br />shell 软件：FinalShell 3.7.7</p></blockquote><hr /><h3 id="下载官方系统镜像"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#下载官方系统镜像"></a> 下载官方系统镜像</h3><blockquote><p>注意：优先使用BT下载，直接下载ios镜像会卡住在99%，下载好BT种子后，用迅雷打开进行下载</p></blockquote><p>直接下载：<a href="https://vault.centos.org/7.5.1804/isos/x86_64/CentOS-7-x86_64-DVD-1804.iso">https://vault.centos.org/7.5.1804/isos/x86_64/CentOS-7-x86_64-DVD-1804.iso</a></p><p>下载BT种子：<a href="https://vault.centos.org/7.5.1804/isos/x86_64/CentOS-7-x86_64-DVD-1804.torrent">https://vault.centos.org/7.5.1804/isos/x86_64/CentOS-7-x86_64-DVD-1804.torrent</a></p><h3 id="安装centos75"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#安装centos75"></a> 安装CentOS7.5</h3><p>打开VMware Workstation 16 Pro点击创建虚拟机</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201215131759457.png" alt="image-20201215131759457" /></p><hr /><h4 id="安装方式一"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#安装方式一"></a> 安装方式一</h4><blockquote><p>使用VMware典型安装，安装步骤简单，默认安装GUI图形界面</p></blockquote><ol><li><p>选择<code>典型</code>安装，点击<code>下一步</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201215132805035.png" alt="image-20201215132805035" /></p></li><li><p>选择<code>安装程序光盘映像文件</code>，点击<code>浏览</code>，找到下载好的<code>镜像文件</code>，然后点击<code>下一步</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201215172400165.png" alt="image-20201215172400165" /></p></li><li><p>输入<code>用户信息</code>，点击<code>下一步</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201215174004271.png" alt="image-20201215174004271" /></p></li><li><p>输入<code>虚拟机名称</code>，点击<code>浏览</code>，然后创建一个<code>空文件夹</code>，并<code>重命名</code>，选择它作为安装文件夹，然后点击<code>下一步</code></p><blockquote><p>注意：要为虚拟机新建一个<code>空文件夹</code>，安装虚拟机不要安装在C盘，C盘土豪请随意</p></blockquote><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201215175149224.png" alt="image-20201215175149224" /></p></li><li><p>设置<code>磁盘大小</code>，选择<code>将虚拟磁盘拆分成多个文件</code>，然后点击<code>下一步</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201215175624092.png" alt="image-20201215175624092" /></p></li><li><p>点击<code>自定义硬件</code>设置CPU个数和核心数以及内存大小，默认1核1G，然后点击<code>完成</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201216094022111.png" alt="image-20201216094022111" /></p></li><li><p>开始安装，耐心等待几分钟</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201216094517023.png" alt="image-20201216094517023" /></p></li><li><p>安装完成，输入密码登录系统</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201216095655741.png" alt="image-20201216095655741" /></p></li><li><p>检测网络<code>ping -c 4 baidu.com</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201216100812035.png" alt="image-20201216100812035" /></p></li><li><p>删除yum.pid，否则yum会无法使用</p></li></ol><blockquote><p>需要使用<code>su root</code>命令切换到root，密码跟安装时设置的用户密码一样</p></blockquote><p>yum被占用：</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201216101158784.png" alt="image-20201216101158784" /></p><p>删除yum.pid文件：</p>   <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rm -rf &#x2F;var&#x2F;run&#x2F;yum.pid</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201216101538013.png" alt="image-20201216101538013" /></p><hr /><h4 id="安装方式二"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#安装方式二"></a> 安装方式二</h4><blockquote><p>自定义安装，可以最小化安装</p></blockquote><ol><li><p>选择<code>自定义</code>安装，点击<code>下一步</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201216171547213.png" alt="image-20201216171547213" /></p></li><li><p>点击<code>下一步</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201216171812412.png" alt="image-20201216171812412" /></p></li><li><p>选择<code>稍后安装操作系统</code>，点击<code>下一步</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201216172000103.png" alt="image-20201216172000103" /></p></li><li><p>选择<code>Linux</code>，然后选择<code>CentOS 7 64 位</code>，点击<code>下一步</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201216172159277.png" alt="image-20201216172159277" /></p></li><li><p>输入<code>虚拟机名称</code>，点击<code>浏览</code>，然后创建一个<code>空文件夹</code>，并<code>重命名</code>，选择它作为安装文件夹，然后点击<code>下一步</code></p><blockquote><p>注意：要为虚拟机新建一个<code>空文件夹</code>，安装虚拟机不要安装在C盘，C盘土豪请随意</p></blockquote><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201216172613298.png" alt="image-20201216172613298" /></p></li><li><p>设置CPU个数和核心数，然后点击<code>下一步</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201216173647516.png" alt="image-20201216173647516" /></p></li><li><p>设置<code>内存大小</code>，然后点击<code>下一步</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201216173946671.png" alt="image-20201216173946671" /></p></li><li><p>选择<code>NAT网络模式</code>，点击<code>下一步</code></p><blockquote><p><strong>bridge</strong>桥接模式相当于你家里的另一台主机，直接连接你家里的网络，<br /><strong>NAT</strong>地址转换模式相当于你主机是一个家用路由器，虚拟机是你主机虚拟路由器下的设备<br /><strong>Host-only</strong>独立主机模式相当于没联网的家用路由器，所有虚拟机和主机之间可以通信，虚拟机不能联网</p></blockquote><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201216174719112.png" alt="image-20201216174719112" /></p></li><li><p>选择<code>LSI Logic</code>，点击<code>下一步</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201217102538506.png" alt="image-20201217102538506" /></p></li><li><p>选择<code>SCSI</code>，点击<code>下一步</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201217102708755.png" alt="image-20201217102708755" /></p></li><li><p>选择<code>创建新虚拟磁盘</code>，点击<code>下一步</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201217102842848.png" alt="image-20201217102842848" /></p></li><li><p>设置<code>磁盘大小</code>，选择<code>将虚拟磁盘拆分成多个文件</code>，点击<code>下一步</code></p><blockquote><p>不要选择立即分配所有空间！</p></blockquote><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201217103424100.png" alt="image-20201217103424100" /></p></li><li><p>直接点击<code>下一步</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201217103842266.png" alt="image-20201217103842266" /></p></li><li><p>点击<code>自定义硬件</code></p><blockquote><p>必须点击自定义硬件选择系统镜像，不然无法安装！</p></blockquote><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201217104559353.png" alt="image-20201217104559353" /></p></li><li><p>选择<code>新 CD/DVD(IDE)</code>，选择<code>使用IOS映像文件</code>，点击<code>浏览</code>，选中下载好的<code>系统镜像</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201217104856597.png" alt="image-20201217104856597" /></p></li><li><p>点击<code>完成</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201217132857959.png" alt="image-20201217132857959" /></p></li><li><p>点击<code>开启此虚拟机</code>，开始进行安装，然后耐心等待</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201217133254047.png" alt="image-20201217133254047" /></p></li><li><p>选择<code>语言</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201213191644039.png" alt="image-20201213191644039" /></p></li><li><p>点击选择<code>安装位置</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201213191931700.png" alt="image-20201213191931700" /></p></li><li><p>点击完成，使用默认的自动配置分区即可</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201213192036294.png" alt="image-20201213192036294" /></p></li><li><p>可点击<code>软件选择</code>，选择图形界面和其他软件，默认是最小安装，请自行根据需要进行选择</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201217134556584.png" alt="image-20201217134556584" /></p></li><li><p>点击<code>开始安装</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201213192133172.png" alt="image-20201213192133172" /></p></li><li><p>设置<code>Root密码</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201213192256290.png" alt="image-20201213192256290" /></p></li><li><p>输入<code>密码</code>，点击<code>完成</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201213192448467.png" alt="image-20201213192448467" /></p></li><li><p>耐心等待安装完成，几分钟即可</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201213192523404.png" alt="image-20201213192523404" /></p></li><li><p>安装完成，点击<code>重启</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201213192739375.png" alt="image-20201213192739375" /></p></li><li><p>重启后进入如下界面则安装成功，自行输入root及密码进行登录</p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201213192836514.png" alt="image-20201213192836514" /></p></li></ol><hr /><h3 id="配置网络"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#配置网络"></a> 配置网络</h3><blockquote><p>使用安装方式一可以不用配置，使用<code>ip a</code>可以查看网络信息<br />使用安装方式二最小安装需要配置网络才能联网</p></blockquote><ol><li><p>打开<code>虚拟网络编辑器</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201217135849096.png" alt="image-20201217135849096" /></p></li><li><p>查看VMware虚拟网络NAT模式的<code>IP池</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201213193805125.png" alt="image-20201213193805125" /></p></li><li><p>查看<code>网关</code></p><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201213194033014.png" alt="image-20201213194033014" /></p></li><li><p>编辑<code>配置文件</code></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vi &#x2F;etc&#x2F;sysconfig&#x2F;network-scripts&#x2F;ifcfg-ens33</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改和添加如下配置</p><blockquote><p>IPADDR需要在第二步的IP池内，NETMASK一般都是255.255.255.0，在第二步可以看见，GATEWAY在第三步，DNS1使用114.114.114.114即可</p></blockquote><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/20201220173159.png" alt="image-20201220172945619" /></p></li><li><p>重启网卡</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">service network restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201213194836851.png" alt="image-20201213194836851" /></p></li><li><p>查看结果</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ip a</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/20201220173046.png" alt="image-20201220173044997" /></p></li></ol><h3 id="使用shell软件连接"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#使用shell软件连接"></a> 使用Shell软件连接</h3><ul><li><p>连接成功</p><blockquote><p>此处使用的是<a href="https://www.hostbuf.com/">FinalShell</a>，自行选择自己喜欢的shell软件就好</p></blockquote><p><img src= "/img/loading.gif" data-lazy-src="https://source.accepted.fun/image/article/image-20201213195541720.png" alt="image-20201213195541720" /></p></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
